  "spermWhaleModuleTitle": "Whale Approaching Settings",
  "spermWhaleModuleHelpTitle": "Whale Approaching",
  "spermWhaleModuleParameters": "Parameters",
  "spermWhaleModuleHelpOverview": "Overview",
  "spermWhaleModuleHelpOverviewBody": "This module is used to configure parameters related to the special marine creature \"Whale\", and is typically used in Underwater World levels. As krill begin appearing, the whale will circle above the lawn and trigger the corresponding red subtitle warning. Once at least 3 krill are present on the lawn, the whale will officially appear in the upper-left corner of the lawn. The whale will prioritize swallowing existing krill before continuously sucking up and swallowing plants on the lawn. The rotenone released by Puffy Derris can be inhaled by the whale; after the first inhalation, the whale’s swallowing speed will decrease. Once the number of inhalations reaches the configured rotenone trigger count, the whale will be forced to retreat. Note that the whale can only appear once per level.",
  "spermWhaleModuleHelpFieldsTitle": "Parameter Overview",
  "spermWhaleModuleHelpFieldsBody": "Swallow Interval (SwallowInterval) refers to the interval between the whale’s swallowing actions under normal conditions.\nPoisoned Swallow Interval (PoisonSwallowInterval) refers to the interval between swallowing actions after the whale inhales rotenone once.\nSwallow Duration (SwallowDuration) refers to the total amount of time the whale remains on the lawn sucking up and swallowing plants.\nPoison Trigger Count (PoisonTriggerCount) refers to the number of rotenone inhalations required to force the whale to retreat.",
  "spermWhaleModuleSwallowInterval": "Swallow Interval (SwallowInterval, unit: seconds)",
  "spermWhaleModuleHelpSwallowInterval": "The interval between two swallowing actions under normal conditions.",
  "spermWhaleModulePoisonSwallowInterval": "Rotenone Swallow Interval (PoisonSwallowInterval, unit: seconds)",
  "spermWhaleModuleHelpPoisonSwallowInterval": "The interval between two swallowing actions after the whale inhales rotenone.",
  "spermWhaleModuleSwallowDuration": "Swallow Duration (SwallowDuration, unit: seconds)",
  "spermWhaleModuleHelpSwallowDuration": "The total duration the whale remains on the lawn sucking up and swallowing plants.",
  "spermWhaleModulePoisonTriggerCount": "Rotenone trigger count (PoisonTriggerCount)",
  "spermWhaleModuleHelpPoisonTriggerCount": "The cumulative number of rotenone inhalations required to force the whale to retreat.",
  "spermWhaleModuleNotDeepSeaWarning": "This module is recommended for use in Underwater World lawns. The grid belows only reflects the current lawn configuration; using this module on non-20,000 Leagues Under the Sea/Atlantis lawns may cause compatibility issues.",
