  "eventHelpBeachStageBody": "Zombies emerge from beneath the water. Commonly used for Snorkel Zombies in Big Wave Beach or for zombies that appear during low tide.\nSimilar to Parachute Rain, zombies will spawn in batches. You can specify the total number and spawn range.\nOnly one type of zombie can be used per event. To include multiple types, you need to add multiple events.",
  "eventHelpTidalChangeBody": "This event is used to change the tide position during the selected wave. The range of tide changes cannot exceed the bounds of the lawn.",
  "eventTideWave": "Event: Ocean Currents",
  "eventHelpTideWaveBody": "Creates ocean currents that push the submarine and grant speed boosts to zombies. Commonly used in Underwater World – 20,000 Leagues Under the Sea levels.",
  "tideWaveHelpType": "Direction",
  "eventHelpTideWaveType": "Left: Currents come from the left, pushing the submarine right and speeding up zombies on the left side.\nRight: Currents come from the right, pushing the submarine left and speeding up zombies on the right side.",
  "tideWaveHelpParams": "Notes",
  "eventHelpTideWaveParams": "Unless otherwise specified, the submarine returns to its original position after the duration ends. Plants cannot be planted on the submarine while it is moving.",
  "tideWaveType": "Direction (Type)",
