  "moduleTitle_ZombossFinalStageTimeLimitedChallengeProperties": "Final stage time limit",
  "moduleDesc_ZombossFinalStageTimeLimitedChallengeProperties": "Enables the final zomboss desperation timer. Add or remove only — the timer value comes from the zomboss property sheet (e.g. ZombossFinalStageTimeLimited on Qin Shi Huang props), not from module parameters.",
