  "moduleTitle_RiftThemeDemoModuleProperties": "Theme Configuration",
  "moduleDesc_RiftThemeDemoModuleProperties": "Adds theme effects from Penny's Pursuit, Memory Lane, and other game modes to the level",
  "riftThemeModuleTitle": "Theme Configuration",
  "riftThemeHelpTitle": "Theme Configuration module",
  "riftThemeHelpOverview": "This module defines a list of themes for the level. Themes are global conditions found in modes such as Penny's Pursuit, Memory Lane, and Secret Realm. Each theme provides unique effects. For detailed descriptions of individual themes, please refer to the wiki.gg pages covering those themes.",
  "riftThemeHelpUsage": "Usage",
  "riftThemeHelpUsageBody": "Click the button in the lower-right corner to open the theme selection screen. Themes can be added to or removed from the theme list by clicking them. Once all settings are complete, click the button again to confirm. Themes take effect in the order they appear in the list.",
