  "pvz1PassageFieldTransferCooldown": "Same-zombie teleport cooldown (transferCooldown, unit: seconds)",
  "pvz1PassageHelpTransferCooldown": "The minimum time between two teleports of the same zombie. If set too low, a zombie that fails to leave the portal tile within the interval may be teleported back to the original portal again once the cooldown ends.",
  "pvz1PassageFieldRefreshTime": "Portal reposition interval (refreshTime, unit: seconds)",
  "pvz1PassageHelpRefreshTime": "The interval at which portal positions are regenerated. Portals are refreshed one at a time, meaning each refresh only changes the position of one portal within the same type.",
  "pvz1PassagePortalSpawnPreview": "Portal spawn column preview",
  "pvz1PassageHelpPreview": "Spawn Range Preview",
